  "text": "Among the main findings of the present study conducted in the ICU of two Brazilian teaching hospitals, we highlight that most members of the multi-professional team had knowledge about the potential benefits of EM, including the maintenance of muscle strength and a shorter duration of MV, and that most participants agreed that the benefits of EM exceed the risks to patients under MV. Similar results were reported in a previous study [CITATION_1] that analyzed the knowledge and attitudes of multi-professional health team members involved in care delivery to critically ill patients.",
